doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=0")
    title Shaun Byrne: Full Stack Product Designer
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='src/css/style.css')
    script(async src="https://unpkg.com/scrollreveal/dist/scrollreveal.min.js")
      
  body
    section.intro
      .container
        h1.intro Shaun Byrne 
        p.about Full stack product designer 10+ years working in global digital product teams. I thrive on bringing multidisciplinary teams together to deliver products through design thinking and lean UX principles. 

        a.scroll(href="#section-two") 👇

    section.my-expereince#section-two
      .swiper-container
        .swiper-wrapper
          .swiper-slide
            .container
              h1.reveal My Strengths
              p.reveal I've learnt many things over my career. Here is some of the strengths I value the most. 
              p 👉
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 I Design Things 
              p I've an inherit need to fulfill uswers needs with beautiful flows and journeys. I really enjoy doing it collaborativly with other designers and product teams. 
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 Data Informed
              p I value the entire spectrum of qualitative and quantitaitve data to make better decisions.  
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 Team Player
              p Collective knowledge solves problems much better. I prefer solving my problems with great humans around me, together. 
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 Bridger of Gaps
              p I've spent much of my time across the entire product development cycle. I've developed an empathy for each stage that enables better team delivery.
              
        .swiper-pagination
        
        .swiper-button-next
        .swiper-button-prev

    section.contact
      .container.reveal
        h1.reveal Interested in a chat?
        p.reveal Currently I am focused on my role at #[a.redbubble(href="http://www.redbubble.com") Redbubble], but I always have time for a ☕️ or 💬. Get in contact if you want to learn more about me, my work, or you want really good Melbourne café suggestions. 
        a.button.reveal(href="mailto:byrnecore+portfolio@gmail.com") 👍🏻 Yep, let's chat

    section.social
      .container.reveal
        .social-profiles
          h1.reveal Learn more about me
          p.reveal To see what my life is about, here are all my social profiles 😱. You might even find some of my professional work too. 
          .links.reveal
            a.profile.behance(href='https://www.behance.net/shaunbyrne')
            a.profile.dribbble(href='https://dribbble.com/byrnecore')
            a.profile.linkedin(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/byrneshaun')  
            a.profile.github(href='https://github.com/byrnecore')  
            a.profile.medium(href='https://medium.com/@byrnecore')  
            a.profile.instagram(href='http://instagram.com/byrnecore')  
            a.profile.spotify(href='https://open.spotify.com/user/1274498741')  
            a.profile.twitter(href='https://twitter.com/byrnecore')  
            a.profile.pinterest(href='https://www.pinterest.com.au/byrnecore/') 
            
    section.footer
      .container
        p Designed and built by #[a(href="#") Shaun Byrne] © 2017 | Melbourne, 🇦🇺, 🌏.



